Class DataCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.feed.gtfsRt.DataCache

  • public class DataCache
extends java.lang.Object
    For caching GTFS-realtime messages. Useful because the messages are huge and take a lot of resources so if get multiple requests not too far apart then it makes sense to return a cached version.
